snippet.title: DUNGEON ENCOUNTERS | Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
From the design team behind iconic FINAL FANTASY titles, Dungeon Encounters is a unique dungeon exploration RPG in which you lead an expedition to chart the depths of an otherworldly labyrinth. Plan and prepare to overcome numerous obstacles, solve puzzles, and defeat monsters.

Do you have what it takes to overcome the numerous trials that await you and discover the dungeon's secrets?
Strategize to survive!

Dungeon Encounters is available October 14 on Nintendo Switch ™, Playstation®4 and Steam®!

Enjoy 20% off when you pre-purchase Dungeon Encounters on Nintendo Switch™ and Steam®! - offer available until October 14.
